ware development in Java&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Strong experience in building sophisticated microservice-based applications&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2+ years hands-on experience in a software design role employing a variety of technologies&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2+ years experience as a technical lead&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ability to communicate clearly and effectively, and collaborate with other disciplines&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Solid technical writing skills&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience working on enterprise business applications&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience in building cloud-based applications on platforms such as Amazon Web Services&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;B.Tech/B.E. &amp;nbsp;or greater in computer science or related area OR equivalent experience&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Experience and interest in working in fast-paced environments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience developing a product in an Agile development environme

