, high performance and scalable code across different frameworks and languages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span&gt;Work in fast paced Agile teams and ability to quickly learn and adapt to new tools and technologies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span&gt;Work with QA teams to align on test planning and help in test executions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;b&gt;Candidates must possess the following skills and traits:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span&gt;4 to 6 years of experience with at least 1 year hands on experience with writing SQL queries.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span&gt;Expertise in Java &amp;amp; Javascript &amp;amp; SQL.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt

